request.description:
Endpoint api ini digunakan untuk mendapatkan seluruh data role yang ada.

Contoh response

``` json
{
    "data": [
        {
            "id": "1faf8280-0810-4d13-81e0-9a6168f6a30b",
            "name": "super admin",
            "access": {
                "level": 1
            },
            "created_at": "2024-02-07T05:36:25.104+07:00",
            "updated_at": "2024-02-07T05:36:25.104+07:00"
        }
    ],
    "status": "success"
}
 ```

Endpoint ini digunakan untuk membuat role baru

name: string | required

access: json | required

Contoh response

``` json
{
    "data": {
        "id": "475aa1fe-8fd9-4070-a25b-9ba1fc899aa0",
        "name": "super admin",
        "access": {
            "level": 1
        },
        "created_at": "2024-02-10T11:50:55.693+07:00",
        "updated_at": "2024-02-10T11:50:55.693+07:00"
    },
    "status": "success"
}

 ```

Endpoint ini digunakan untuk mendapatkan role berdasarkan path param id role yang dicari.

contoh response:

``` json
{
    "data": {
        "id": "",
        "name": "",
        "access": {
            "level": 0
        },
        "created_at": "",
        "updated_at": ""
    },
    "status": ""
}

 ```

Endpoint ini digunakan untuk melakukan update nama dan accsess role

contoh response

``` json
{
    "data": {
        "id": "1faf8280-0810-4d13-81e0-9a6168f6a30b",
        "name": "admin update",
        "access": {
            "level": 2
        },
        "created_at": "0001-01-01T00:00:00Z",
        "updated_at": "0001-01-01T00:00:00Z"
    },
    "status": "success"
}
 ```
